How to make the APK
1. Click Export
2. Export Android Application
3. Choose this project
4. Set up the location with password
5. Export on the designated location and you get the APK.

How to use it.
1. Click "Take a photo" to take a photo
2. After you take the photo, you will get some of information such as location
3. You can do more parts such as edit comment, edit vocal comment, delete the photo,
play vocal comment, check comment, and such.
4. And when you move back, you will see collection of photos that you took 
and click into it to see more information of each photo.

